sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User A
    participant UI as TripChat / ChatInput
    participant Service as chatService
    participant Stream as Stream Chat
    participant Hook as useStreamTripChat
    participant SB as Supabase Realtime
    participant Sys as systemMessageService
    participant Other as User B (other client)

    U->>UI: Send "hello"
    UI->>Service: send(message)
    Service->>Stream: channel.sendMessage(text)
    Stream-->>Stream: persist
    Stream-->>Hook: message.new (echo)
    Hook-->>UI: append to local state
    Stream-->>Other: message.new (fan-out)

    Note over Sys: Domain event (poll close, task done)
    Sys->>Stream: channel.sendMessage({silent, skip_push, custom_fields})
    Stream-->>Hook: message.new (system)
    Hook-->>UI: render SystemMessageBubble inline

    Note over SB: Adjacent realtime updates
    SB-->>Hook: postgres_changes on message_reactions
    Hook-->>UI: re-render reactions
